entry.title: https://github.com/7h30th3r0n3/Evil-M5Project
entry.content: Evil-M5Project is an innovative tool developed for ethical testing and exploration of WiFi networks. It's compatible with Cardputer, Atoms3, Fire, core2. You can scan, monitor, and interact with WiFi networks in a controlled environment. This project is designed for educational purposes, aiding in understanding network security and vulnerabilities.

entry.title: https://github.com/erew123/alltalk_tts
entry.content: AllTalk is based on the Coqui TTS engine, similar to the Coqui_tts extension for Text generation webUI, however supports a variety of advanced features, such as a settings page, low VRAM support, DeepSpeed, narrator, model finetuning, custom models, wav file maintenance. It can also be used with 3rd Party software via JSON calls.
